joe.util.bootstrap
Interface PropertySupplier

public interface PropertySupplier

Abstraction over property generators. Properties belong to a property group, and property groups have a priority ordering. In descending priority, these are:

  1. System properties
  2. User properties
  3. Machine-local properties
  4. IDE properties
  5. Environment properties (dev, prod, ...)

Author:
Joe Kearney
